  <h3> My top 3 movies of all-time</h3>
  <hr>
  <h3>Fast and Furios 5</h3>
  <p>This is one of my favorite movies. <br> The film follows a team of street racers who use their skills to fight crime.  <br>The film is known for the action, speed and cars with which the races took place in the film. <br></p>


  <h3>Ford vs Ferrari</h3>
  <p>This film highlights the engineering ingenuity in the automotive industry. <br> 
    The film follows the true story of the rivalry between Ford and Ferrari during the 1960s. <br></p>



  <h3>Top gun</h3>
  <p>This film follows a military pilot, Maverick, who is trained at an elite aviator school. <br>
    The film is known for its thrilling dogfights and Maverick's struggle with his ego and the loss of his friends. <br></p>
  
  
